íźźŕTitle: This week in Nushell #95
Path: Package news
Content:
You can now install Nushell directly from the 
[link: https://github.com/microsoft/winget-pkgs/tree/master/manifests/n/Nushell/Nushell/0.32.0] official winget packages
 using 
``winget install nu``
.
óŔRarchive/external_nushell_repo_backup/nushell.github.io/blog/2021-06-18-twin0095.mdŔ@5bca0b751701cc375044f0cf2e0ed552d1bfba7dc36b359b9b21295b177c0657łThis week in Nushell #95ĎßNushellŕ	
andrasio 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3645] cleaned up nu-completion dependencies.
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3632] supported version option in Nu bin.
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3631] extracted completions into subcrate.
, connected 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3624] Nu's rest arguments are source(s) files scripts to run.
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3621] removeed 'help' Nu bin positional support.
, and updated 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3619] Nu to bootstrap itself from main.
jonathandturner 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3644] fixed the ignore example
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3643] relaxed groups and blocks to output at pipeline level
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3642] fixed issue in external subexpression paths
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3639] added back disks and net to sys
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3627] added file not found error for nu cmd args
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3612] refactored rarely changing engine state into its own struct
chrisfinazzo fixed a 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3635] Shellcheck issue
fdncred 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3634] fixed FlatShape::Garbage's default foreground color
vladdoster added 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3630] (docs) update README.md
NiklasJonsson fixed the parser to 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3628] only discard command comment if prev token was comment
reaganmcf added 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3618] Plugin: from_mp4 and UntaggedValue::duration fix
itsme-alan 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3615] added winget installation instructions 
voanhduy1512 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3613] fixed syntax hightlight when using Circumflex-Operator
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3611] added support to run external command with string evaluation
elferherrera added 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3608] dataframe commands
sambordo1 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3607] ported mkdir to engine-p
